programme.title: Emanet

programme.title: The Internship
programme.desc: Billy and Nick are two old school salesmen who embark into a daring challenge, when they start an internship at Google, as they struggle to beat tech-savvy geniuses for a shot to be hired.

programme.desc: A small Wisconsin town becomes the center of political attention, when a Democrat strategist named Gary tries to help a retired Marine Colonel run for mayor.

programme.desc: A look into the life of Dick Cheney, vice president to George W. Bush and one of the most influential figures in American and global politics. programme.title: Bombshell
programme.desc: A group of women try to take on Fox News head, Roger Ailes, due to his administration policy and the toxic male culture he is spreading in the network.

programme.title: Miss Sloane
programme.desc: A successful lobbyist finds herself in the fight of her life when she puts her strategic talents into trying to push for legislation to control guns. programme.title: Our Brand Is Crisis

programme.title: Jackie
programme.desc: A look into the aftermath of JFKs assassination and the tremendous struggle his wife Jacqueline Kennedy found herself facing. programme.title: The Campaign
programme.desc: Two businessmen are trying to get the US Congressman Cam (Will Ferrell) out of the way ahead of the next election in an attempt to take control of the North Carolina area and gain greater power, by pushing Marty Huggins (Zach Galifianakis) to run against him.
